  "text": "What was its purpose for that? It was a drone designed to listen to the various signals of your pupils. You were at that time beginning work in a more technical sphere. We were interested in determining the extent and the rapidity of your advances. This drone was powered by a simple fission, a motor or engine as you would call it. It was not that type which you now know, but was very small. However, it has the same destructive effect upon earth density molecular structures. Thus, as it malfunctioned, we felt it was best to pick a place for its destruction rather than attempt to retrieve it for the possibility, probability modes of this maneuver looked very, very minute.",
